20Magazine.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20building%20my%20own%20life%20has%20made%20me%20very%20aware%20of%20what%20my%20mother%20built%20on%20her%20own%20and%20what%20it%20took%20for%20her%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20is%20the%20elder%20of%20two%20children%20from%20Diana%20Ross's%20marriage%20to%20music%20executive%20Robert%20Ellis%20Silberstein.%20She%20also%20has%20an%20older%20half-sister%20from%20her%20mother's%20relationship%20with%20Motown%20founder%20Berry%20Gordy%20and%20two%20younger%20half-brothers%20from%20her%20mother's%20second%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20said%20her%20mother's%20success%20inspired%20her%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BMy%20mom%5D%20didn't%20build%20the%20wealth%20she%20has%2C%20she%20didn't%20build%20the%20career%20she%20made%20because%20of%20a%20man.%20The%20example%20that%20was%20set%20for%20me%20%5Bwas%5D%20that%20I%20didn't%20need%20a%20man%20to%20build%20the%20life%20I%20wanted.%20It%20wasn't%2C%20'Look%20at%20me%2C'%20it%20was%2C%20'This%20is%20me.'%20And%20that%20informed%20something%20very%20important%20for%20me%20foundationally%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20comfortable%20alone%20starts%20with%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20how%20to%20care%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKnowing%20how%20to%20care%20for%20yourself%20is%20also%20how%20you%20teach%20someone%20how%20you%20want%20to%20be%20cared%20for.%20I've%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20life%20getting%20to%20know%20who%20I%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20favorite%20place%20to%20be%20is%20inside%20my%20body%2C%20to%20be%20present%20in%20my%20skin%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3BBlack-ish%26quot%3B%20actor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Ross%20is%20content%20on%20her%20own%2C%20she%20says%20she%20is%20still%20open%20to%20love%20and%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20don't%20mind%20is%20being%20a%20poster%20child%20for%20living%20your%20life%20on%20your%20own%20terms%2C%20for%20not%20waiting%20for%20partnership%20to%20find%20joy%20and%20happiness%2C%20for%20curating%20and%20cultivating%20one's%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fself-worth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esense%20of%20self%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20says%20she%20seeks%20a%20partnership%20built%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsomeone-not-working-at-relationship-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emeeting%20as%20equals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20a%20whole%20life%20and%20I%20want%20a%20real%20life%2C%20and%20I%20want%20a%20true%20life%2C%20and%20I%20want%20a%20partner%20that's%20not%20going%20to%20sweep%20me%20off%20my%20feet%2C%20but%20is%20going%20to%20link%20arms%20with%20me.%20And%20that%20might%20not%20happen%2C%20and%20that's%20OK%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Ross%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20actor%20had%20no%20additional%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20appearance%20on%20Michelle%20Obama's%20%26quot%3BIMO%26quot%3B%20podcast%20in%20April%2C%20Ross%20said%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftracee-ellis-ross-prefers-dating-younger-men-age-gap-relationship-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprefers%20dating%20younger%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20men%20her%20age%20are%20often%20%26quot%3Bsteeped%20in%20toxic%20masculinity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20long%20been%20past%20the%20age%20where%20I%20feel%20like%20it's%20my%20job%20to%20teach%20somebody%20or%20grow%20them%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%2C%20I'm%20not%20interested%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20joins%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20women%20who%20have%20spoken%20openly%20about%20finding%20meaning%20in%20singlehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20%26quot%3BCall%20Her%20Daddy%26quot%3