lt%3D%5C%22Jim%20Farley%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Ford%2C%20is%20seen%20holding%20a%20microphone%20and%20speaking.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688ad6be3d5881a51c1e51ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223446%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJim%20Farley%2C%20Ford's%20CEO%2C%20said%20a%20Toyota%204Runner%20made%20in%20Japan%20could%20cost%20%2410%2C000%20less%20than%20a%20Ford%20Bronco%20made%20in%20Michigan.%3Cp%3ETasos%20Katopodis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFord%20is%20projecting%20a%20%242%20billion%20bill%20due%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20tariffs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20is%20%24500%20million%20higher%20than%20what%20it%20forecast%20last%20quarter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFord's%20CEO%20says%20Trump's%20reduced%20tariffs%20on%20Japan%20will%20give%20its%20automakers%20a%20%26quot%3Bmeaningful%26quot%3B%20advantage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ceo-china-ev-progress-most-humbling-thing-ever-seen-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJim%20Farley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Ford%2C%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-automakers-ford-vw-stellantis-respond-layoffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etariff%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20saddle%20the%20automaker%20with%20a%20%242%20billion%20bill%20while%20benefiting%20its%20Japanese%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20tariff%20bill%20is%20%242%20billion%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20net%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20said%20in%20an%20earnings%20call.%20The%20company%20had%20projected%20a%20tariff%20hit%20of%20%241.5%20billion%20in%20its%20last%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarley%20told%20analysts%20he%20expects%20automakers%20to%20adopt%20a%20regional%20rather%20than%20globalized%20approach%20toward%20their%20businesses.%20In%20addition%20to%20tariffs%2C%20Farley%20said%20the%20change%20is%20being%20driven%20by%20the%20rise%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20and%20new%20carbon%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20increasingly%20see%20Europe%2C%20North%20America%2C%20and%20Asia%20becoming%20kind%20of%20regional%20businesses%20with%20tariff%20rates%20that%20are%20aligned%20for%20those%20three%20or%20four%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20quite%20a%20fundamental%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Ford%20and%20the%20White%20House%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarley%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20on%20the%20same%20day%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20reduced%20tariffs%20on%20Japan%20would%20give%20its%20Asian%20rivals%20a%20%26quot%3Bmeaningful%26quot%3B%20cost%20advantage.%20Last%20week%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20the%20US%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-japan-trade-deal-trump-sp500-tsla-goog-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elower%20its%20tariffs%20on%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%2015%25%20from%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reduced%20tariffs%2C%20lower%20labour%20costs%2C%20and%20favorable%20exchange%20rates%20%26quot%3Breally%20advantage%20their%20export%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Kentucky-built%20Ford%20Escape%20could%20cost%20%245%2C000%20more%20than%20a%20Japanese-made%20Toyota%20Rav4%2C%20while%20a%20Michigan-made%20Ford%20Bronco%20might%20be%20undercut%20by%20a%20Toyota%204Runner%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20%2410%2C000%2C%20Farley%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarley%20told%20Bloomberg%20that%20Ford%20is%20working%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20%26quot%3Bminimize%20our%20tariff%20expense%20so%20that%20we%20can%20get%20more%20competitive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20bottom%20line%20is%20our%20plan%20at%20Ford%20is%20not%20to%20compete%20in%20those%20commodity%20segments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Farley%20has%20talked%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-tariffs-could-wipe-out-ford-gms-profits-analysts-say-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echallenges%20Ford%20faces%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20new%20slate%20of%20tariffs.%20Farley%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautomakers-are-revealing-how-much-trumps-tariffs-are-costing-them-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E25%25%20tariff%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bwindfall%20for%20South%20Korean%20and%20Japanese%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20guidance%2C%20we%20can%20handle%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20of%20tariffs.%20If%20it%20goes%20beyond%20that%2C%20obviously%2C%20it%20will%20be%20billions%20and%20billions%20of%20incremental%20profit%20headwinds%20for%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20told%20the%20outlet%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Ford's%20shares%20fell%20by%20nearly%201.6%25%20in%20after-hours%20trading.%20The%20company's%20shares%20are%20up%20by%209.8%25%20year%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-trump-tariffs-cost-2-billion-benefit-japanese-rivals-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753937082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688ad1f1f748d8c055f69956%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-trump-tariffs-cost-2-billion-benefit-japanese-rivals-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jim%20Farley%2C%20Ford's%20CEO%2C%20said%20a%20Toyota%204Runner%20made%20in%20Japan%20could%20cost%20%2410%2C000%20less%20tha