independently%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20brigade's%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHrytsenko%20said%20the%20bike's%20parts%20were%20disassembled%20and%20brought%20to%20a%20nearby%20position%20on%20the%20frontline.%20Afterward%2C%20the%20vehicle%20was%20put%20together%20and%20flown%20to%20the%20soldier%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20in%20HQ%20was%20shouting%20and%20crying%20like%20we'd%20just%20launched%20the%20first%20plane%20in%20the%20sky%2C%26quot%3B%20Hrytsenko%20said%20of%20the%20moment%20when%20the%20bike%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brigade%20also%20showed%20surveillance%20drone%20footage%20of%20a%20soldier%20riding%20an%20e-bike%20through%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHrytsenko%20said%20that%20while%20the%20soldier%20later%20struck%20a%20land%20mine%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20walk%20several%20hundred%20meters%20to%20a%20nearby%20friendly%20position%2C%20where%20drone%20pilots%20flew%20in%20another%20e-bike%20so%20he%20could%20fully%20exit%20the%20combat%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20operation%20cost%20us%20two%20lost%20e-bikes%2C%20around%20100%2C000%2C%20and%20two%20lost%20HeavyShot%20drones%2C%20%2415%2C000%20each%2C%26quot%3B%20Hrytsenko%20said%2C%20likely%20referring%20to%20100%2C000%20hryvnias%2C%20or%20about%20%242%2C340.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brigade%20said%20the%20soldier%20evacuated%20safely%20and%20showed%20interview%20clips%20of%20a%20man%20it%20said%20was%20Tankist.%20BI%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20his%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHrytsenko%20added%20that%20the%20e-bikes%20were%20funded%20via%20donations%20from%20volunteers%2C%20a%20common%20occurrence%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20where%20units%20have%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-dronemakers-war-unwinnable-dirt-cheap-crowdfunding-veterans-civilians-russia-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecrowdfund%20for%20drones%20and%20weapons.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20a%20s