edes-Benz%20representative%20said%20he%20thinks%20demand%20for%20EVs%20will%20pick%20back%20up%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMercedes-Benz%20says%20it%20is%20pausing%20orders%20for%20its%20electric%20vehicles%20as%20demand%20wanes%20among%20American%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20German%20automotive%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20decision%20affects%20all%20variants%20of%20the%20EQS%20Sedan%2C%20EQS%20SUV%2C%20EQE%20Sedan%2C%20and%20the%20EQE%20SUV.%20Vehicles%20that%20were%20scheduled%20for%20production%20before%20September%201%20will%20still%20be%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20company%20with%20global%20activities%20and%20more%20than%2030%20plants%20worldwide%2C%20including%20in%20Alabama%20and%20South%20Carolina%2C%20Mercedes-Benz%20continuously%20optimizes%20its%20production%20network%20and%20uses%20its%20high%20flexibility%20to%20react%20quickly%20to%20market%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20assemble%20all%20of%20our%20models%20meant%20for%20export%20to%20global%20markets%2C%20as%20well%20as%20adapt%20to%20meet%20local%20market%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20it%20cannot%20say%20when%20US%20order%20banks%20for%20EQ%20models%20will%20reopen%20%26quot%3Bfor%20competitive%20reasons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20Q2%20earnings%20report%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Mercedes-Benz%20said%20the%20total%20unit%20sales%20for%20its%20battery%20electric%20vehicles%20(BEV)%20had%20slipped%20by%20almost%2025%25%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20time%20last%20year%3A%2045%2C843%20units%20to%2035%2C027%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Mercedes-Benz%20began%20manufacturing%20two%20all-electric%20vehicle%20models%20%E2%80%94%20the%20EQS%20SUV%20and%20EQE%20SUV%20%E2%80%94%20at%20its%20Alabama%20plant.%20In%202023%2C%20it%20also%20added%20the%20Mercedes-Maybach%20EQS%20SUV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20decision