0are%20the%20things%20he%20shares%20with%20his%20neighbours%20and%20people%20from%20nearby%20villages.%20He%20explains%20why%20the%20soil%20is%20eroding%2C%20how%20chemical%20pesticides%20harm%20the%20land%2C%20and%20how%20unregulated%20prawn%20farming%20is%20eating%20away%20at%20the%20roots%20of%20the%20mangroves.%20There%20are%20no%20charts%20or%20slides%20%E2%80%94%20just%20words%20that%20make%20sense%20to%20the%20people%20listening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202022%2C%20I%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Forest%20Department%E2%80%99s%20mangrove%20reforestation%20initiative%20called%20%E2%80%98Mangrove%20Mitra%E2%80%99.%20We%20convinced%2030%20families%20to%20give%20up%2013%20acres%20of%20non-arable%20land%20near%20the%20river%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20quiet%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20kept%20their%20land%20rights%20and%20received%20compensation.%20Ten%20species%20were%20planted%20%E2%80%94%20Hental%2C%20Guan%2C%20Bani%2C%20Rai%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChildhood%20bond%20turns%20into%20a%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20Nirakar%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20the%20forest%20was%20someone%20who%20saw%20his%20spark%20early%20on%20%E2%80%94%20Madhusmit%20Pati.%20Founder%20of%20Nature%E2%80%99s%20Club%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20has%20been%20active%20in%20Bhitarkanika%20since%201994%2C%20Madhusmit%20has%20spent%20decades%20helping%20people%20prepare%20for%20disasters%2C%20restore%20damaged%20forests%2C%20and%20find%20ways%20to%20earn%20a%20living%20without%20harming%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20Nirakar%20under%20his%20wing%20during%20his%20school%20years%2C%20guiding%20him%20through%20tough%20times%20and%20fanning%20his%20curiosity%20about%20the%20mangroves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20vulnerable%20and%20complex%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20Madhusmit%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThoughtless%20actions%20in%20the%20name%20of%20conservation%20can%20backfire.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%