y%20out%20of%20wage%20labour.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20burgeoning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F403144%2Fhow-to-start-freshwater-pearl-farming-from-scratch-farmers-share-secret-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderstanding%20of%20pearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20scaling%20the%20venture%20became%20the%20next%20logical%20step.%20The%20friends%20expanded%20their%20operations%2C%20setting%20up%20additional%20farms%20of%20one%20lakh%20mussels%20across%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20and%20Daman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20leap%20into%20the%20uncharted%20had%20transformed%20into%20a%20full-blown%20enterprise%2C%20with%20a%20turnover%20reaching%20Rs%201%20crore%20under%20the%20brand%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Pearl%20Farming%E2%80%99.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20their%20brand%20has%20begun%20to%20carve%20its%20name%2C%20selling%20pearls%20both%20domestically%20and%20internationally%20from%20the%20United%20States%20to%20Canada%20and%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETraining%20others%20to%20shine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20duo%20has%20also%20trained%20more%20than%20200%20local%20people%20interested%20in%20taking%20up%20pearl%20farming.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20Santosh%20Kumar%2C%20embarked%20on%20his%20pearl%20farming%20journey%20in%202022%20after%20undertaking%20training%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20experience%2C%20the%20Ambala%20resident%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20two-day%20training%20was%20both%20theoretical%20and%20practical.%20The%20initial%20charges%20of%20Rs%206%2C000%20for%20the%20training%20were%20subtracted%20from%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20equipment%20and%20mussels%20I%20purchased.%20This%20essentially%20made%20the%20training%20free.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20months%20after%20completing%20the%20training%2C%20Santosh%20set%20up%20his%20own%20pearl%20fa