%20funds%20with%20community%20priorities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20began%20with%20pilot%20programmes%20in%20%3Cstrong%3ERamgarh%20and%20Bokaro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20districts%20led%20by%20progressive%20district%20magistrates%20%3Cstrong%3EB%20Rajeshwari%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20%3Cstrong%3ERai%20Mahimapat%20Ray%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(both%202011%20batch%20IAS%20officers).%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20focussed%20on%20figuring%20out%20what%20their%20communities%20needed%20and%20finding%20more%20sustainable%20economic%20opportunities%20for%20them%20aligned%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20(SDGs).%20Soon%2C%20we%20deployed%20our%20fellows%20to%20start%20working%20out%20how%20DMFT%20resources%20could%20be%20aligned%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rwitwika%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20early%20efforts%20triggered%20a%20broader%20response.%20As%20Swaniti%E2%80%99s%20fellows%20embedded%20themselves%20within%20the%20local%20administrations%2C%20more%20district%20officials%20began%20to%20explore%20how%20DMFT%20funds%20could%20better%20serve%20%3Cstrong%3Evulnerable%20groups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20especially%20%3Cstrong%3Einformal%20mining%20workers%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Many%20administrators%20started%20mapping%20out%20economic%20alternatives%20and%20sought%20to%20unlock%20public%20funds%20to%20support%20these%20pathways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20Swaniti%E2%80%99s%20role%20evolved.%20What%20began%20as%20an%20effort%20to%20optimise%20DMFT%20usage%20expanded%20to%20include%20convergence%20with%20other%20State%20and%20Union%20government%20schemes.%20The%20focus%20shifted%20towards%20%3Cstrong%3Eenabling%20a%20%E2%80%98just%20transition%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94ensuring%20that%20communities%20dependent%20on%20fossil%20fuel%20economies%20weren%E2%80%99t%20left%20behind%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20shift%20to%20a%20more%20sustainable%2C%20inclusive%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753712058.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pilot%20projects%20in%20Ramgarh%20and%20Bokaro%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20first%20just%20transition%20model.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753712058.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753712058-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753712058-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753712058-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-2_11zon-1-1753712058-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477383%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPilot%20projects%20in%20Ramgarh%20and%20Bokaro%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20first%20just%20transition%20model.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20those%20small%20pilots%20in%20Ramgarh%20and%20Bokaro%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20what%20is%20now%20known%20as%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EJH-RESET%20Project%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20initiative%20rooted%20in%20systemic%20reform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20an%20organisation%20was%20working%20without%20significant%20philanthropic%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rwitwika.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20philanthropic%20support%20came%20for%20the%20deployment%20of%20Swaniti%E2%80%99s%20technical%20team%20in%20the%20field.%20The%20funding%20required%20to%20run%20these%20programmes%20for%20local%20communities%20came%20from%20government-sponsored%20schemes.%20Our%20task%20was%20to%20help%20them%20identify%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20community%2C%20map%20out%20where%20public%20funds%20are%20needed%20and%20mobilise%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EGaurav%20Bhattacharya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20consultant%20with%20the%20Swaniti%20Initiative%2C%20recalls%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20their%20work%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20coal%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20we%20ended%20up%20having%20a%20presence%20across%20all%20mining%20districts%2C%20in%20the%20initial%20months%2C%20our%20team%20was%20actually%20working%20on%20unlocking%20those%20funds%2C%20which%20were%20present%20at%20the%20DMFT-level%20in%20Ramgarh%20and%20Bokaro%20districts.%20The%20DMFT%20fund%20is%20split%20between%20high-priority%20and%20non-priority%20areas.%20So%2C%20our%20team%20did%20a%20mapping%20exercise%20to%20identify%20high%20priority%20and%20low%20priority%20areas%20and%20where%20there%20is%20the%20highest%20amount%20of%20underutilised%20funds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mapping%20DMFT%20funds%20revealed%20untapped%20resources%20that%20could%20be%20channelled%20to%20empower%20smallholder%20farmers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477391%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMapping%20DMFT%20funds%20revealed%20untapped%20resources%20that%20could%20be%20channelled%20to%20empower%20smallholder%20farmers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mapping%20exercise%20revealed%20a%20crucial%20insight%3A%20%3Cstrong%3EDMFT%20funds%20could%20support%20smallholder%20farmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20especially%20in%20regions%20where%20other%20public%20financing%20remained%20underutilised.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Horticulture%20was%20running%20promising%20programmes%20involving%20%3Cstrong%3Esolar-powered%20cold%20storages%20and%20dryers%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20our%20mapping%20exercise%2C%20we%20found%20that%20some%20of%20these%20funds%20can%20be%20tapped%20for%20smallholder%20farmers.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Horticulture%20was%20actually%20leading%20a%20lot%20of%20programmes%20on%20solar-powered%20cold%20storages%20and%20dryers%20for%20farmers.%20We%20felt%20that%20if%20we%20could%20kind%20of%20mobilise%20this%20fund%2C%20then%20we%20would%20be%20able%20to%20procure%20these%20products%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20department%20and%20distribute%20them%20to%20farmer%20producer%20organisations%20(FPOs).%20For%20the%20first%20cycle%20of%20procurement%2C%20we%20included%20a%20buyback%20clause%2C%20i.e.%20the%20vendor%20selling%20the%20equipment%20is%20also%20responsible%20for%20buying%20the%20first%20cycle%20of%20produce%20harvested%20by%20farmers%20in%20these%20FPOs%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gaurav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20clause%20aimed%20to%20incentivise%20the%20adoption%20of%20solar%20drying%20technology%20and%20ensure%20early%20returns%20for%20farmers.%20Starting%20with%20%3Cstrong%3ERamgarh%20and%20Bokaro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20model%20soon%20expanded%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EDumka%2C%20Chaibasa%2C%20Latehar%2C%20and%20Chatra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94the%20latter%20emerging%20as%20the%20most%20successful%20district%20in%20mobilising%20public%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solar%20dryers%20with%20buyback%20guarantees%20helped%20farmers%20adopt%20technology%20and%20secure%20early%20profits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477395%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolar%20dryers%20with%20buyback%20guarantees%20helped%20farmers%20adopt%20technology%20and%20secure%20early%20profits.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20core%20implementation%20of%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EJH-RESET%20project%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20took%20place%20between%202020%20and%202023%2C%20its%20foundation%20was%20laid%20as%20early%20as%202018%E2%80%9319.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20solar%20dryers%20alone%2C%20Swaniti%20reports%20a%20%3Cstrong%3Emonthly%20income%20increase%20of%20%E2%82%B93%2C000%E2%80%93%E2%82%B94%2C000%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20mobilised%20about%20%E2%82%B955%20crore%20from%20three%20types%20of%20public%20funds%E2%80%94DMFT%2C%20SCF%20(State%20Co-operative%20Federation)%20and%20the%20Aspirational%20District%20Programme%20(ADP).%20This%20money%20was%20utilised%20to%20procure%20solar-powered%20cold%20storage%20and%20dryers.%20There%20was%20one%20cold%20storage%20facility%20distributed%20for%20three%20FPOs%2C%20and%20the%20solar%20dryers%20were%20allocated%20to%20each%20FPO.%20We%20had%20an%20active%20cohort%20of%20about%20200%20farmers%2C%20largely%20involved%20in%20growing%20tomatoes%2C%20given%20that%20it%20is%20the%20crop%20with%20the%20highest%20price%20slippage.%20With%20access%20to%20a%20dryer%20and%20cold%20storage%2C%20farmers%20saw%20the%20overall%20annual%20income%20of%20these%20smallholder%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20solar%20dryer%2C%20supplied%20by%20vendors%2C%20costs%20approximately%20%E2%82%B918%E2%80%93%E2%82%B919%20lakhs.%20Distribution%20took%20place%20in%20%3Cstrong%3Ethree%20phases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20starting%20with%20DMFT%20support%2C%20followed%20by%20funding%20from%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EDirectorate%20of%20Horticulture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EAspirational%20District%20Programme%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%20Rs%2055%20crore%20was%20mobilised%20to%20install%20solar%20dryers%20and%20cold%20storages%2C%20boosting%20farmer%20incomes%20across%20Jharkhand.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477409%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%20Rs%2055%20crore%20was%20mobilised%20to%20install%20solar%20dryers%20and%20cold%20storages%2C%20boosting%20farmer%20incomes%20across%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20us%20almost%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20from%20the%20date%20of%20releasing%20the%20expression%20of%20interest%20to%20finding%20adequate%20vendors%2C%20to%20changing%20the%20RFP%20policy%20and%20then%20finally%20doing%20the%20demonstration.%20Although%20willingness%20and%20resources%20were%20often%20available%2C%20our%20program%20delivery%20designs%20tended%20to%20be%20overly%20complex%20and%20to%20cause%20delays%20in%20funding.%20The%20year%202020%E2%80%9321%20was%20spent%20on%20getting%20these%20dryers%20and%20cold%20storages%20out%2C%20followed%20by%20six%20months%20of%20demonstrations%20from%20private%20vendors%20to%20FPOs%2C%20showing%20farmers%20how%20to%20use%20this%20equipment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gaurav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20implementation%2C%20farmers%20were%20trained%20to%20use%20the%20new%20technology.%20%3Cstrong%3EAbdul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Latehar%2C%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20received%20a%20few%20training%20sessions%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20solar%20dryer%20and%20how%20to%20cut%20tomatoes.%20During%20the%20installation%20phase%2C%20they%20also%20provided%20extensive%20training%20on%20each%20part%20and%20how%20to%20use%20it%20correctly.%E2%80%9D%20Two%20private%20vendors%20were%20ultimately%20chosen%20to%20supply%20the%20solar%20equipment%20after%20a%20rigorous%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20designed%20the%20technical%20eligibility%20criteria%20to%20determine%20which%20vendors%20we%20would%20use%20to%20distribute%20this%20solar%20equipment%2C%20which%20included%20having%20experience%20working%20with%20at%20least%2010%20FPOs%20and%20implementing%20five%20social%20programmes%2C%20among%20others.%20We%20started%20with%2011%20vendors%20putting%20in%20their%20bids%2C%20but%20eventually%20only%20two%20were%20left%20standing%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gaurav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1753712769.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmers%20were%20trained%20extensively%20to%20operate%20solar%20dryers%2C%20ensuring%20smooth%20adoption%20of%20new%20technology.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1753712769.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1753712769-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1753712769-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1753712769-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1753712769-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477413%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFarmers%20were%20trained%20extensively%20to%20operate%20solar%20dryers%2C%20ensuring%20smooth%20adoption%20of%20new%20technology.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20tomatoes%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Elemongrass%2C%20oilseed%20cultivation%2C%20and%20cage-fishing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20also%20emerged%20as%20valuable%20income%20sources%20for%20farmers%20under%20this%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20the%20aim%20was%20never%20just%20about%20higher%20yields.%20As%20%3Cstrong%3ERwitwika%20Bhattacharya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20clarifies%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20to%20look%20at%20bringing%20in%20non-polluting%20solutions%20to%20increase%20the%20economic%20value%20of%20farmers.%20Through%20the%20entire%20JH-RESET%20project%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20working%20towards%20the%20larger%20goal%20of%20just%20transition%20for%20the%20cohort%20of%20these%20mining%20workers%2C%20SHG%20workers%20or%20agriculture%20workers%20whose%20livelihood%2C%20economy%20and%20everything%20depends%20on%20mining%20today.%20See%2C%20these%20mines%20will%20close%20one%20day.%20Some%20of%20the%20mines%20will%20get%20shut%20down%20because%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20promote%20renewable%20solutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20would%20then%20happen%20with%20these%20entire%20sets%20of%20workers%3F%20Are%20they%20skilled%20enough%20to%20take%20up%20alternate%20work%3F%20That%20is%20why%20a%20part%20of%20the%20JH-RESET%20project%20is%20also%20to%20train%20the%20people%20on%20using%20solar%20dryers%2C%20solar%20pumps%2Firrigation%20systems%20or%20become%20solar%20entrepreneurs.%20The%20base%20of%20this%20programme%20has%20always%20been%20to%20increase%20the%20economic%20value%20of%20stakeholders%20like%20smallholder%20farmers%2C%20but%20it%20is%20built%20on%20solutions%20which%20come%20in%20the%20renewable%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025