friend%20and%20found%20it%20interesting.%20We%20spent%20time%20understanding%20the%20process%20of%20this%20construction%20and%20decided%20it%20was%20the%20right%20one%20to%20go%20ahead%20with.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Vijayaprabhu%20and%20Haripriya%20opted%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328655%2Fsunnymead-eco-friendly-earthquake-resistant-homestay-in-shimla-built-with-dhajji-dewari-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emud%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20intrigue%2C%20to%20Revathi%20it%20held%20a%20personal%20allure.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20born%20in%20a%20mud%20home%20in%20my%20native%20village%20and%20always%20wanted%20to%20go%20back%20to%20my%20roots.%20Mud%20houses%20have%20a%20direct%20connection%20with%20nature%20and%20induce%20a%20natural%20living%20experience.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirudh%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20take%20it%20on.%20Designing%20a%20farm%20stay%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20a%20forest%20is%20not%20a%20project%20one%20comes%20across%20every%20day.%20As%20he%20describes%20the%20features%20of%20the%20farm%20stay%20spread%20across%20the%20four-acre%20land%2C%20one%20can%20tell%20how%20seamlessly%20the%20raw%20finesse%20of%20the%20property%20blends%20into%20the%20surrounding%20foliage.%20A%20process%20that%20lasted%20over%20two%20years%20saw%20the%20light%20of%20day%20six%20months%20ago%20when%20Anirudh%20handed%20the%20keys%20over%20to%20the%20trio.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20design%20philosophy%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20typical%20South%20Indian%20traditional%20home%20with%20a%20courtyard%20that%20would%20wrap%20itself%20around%20the%20front%20of%20the%20house.%20The%20courtyard%20would%20be%20a%20communal%20sit-out%20area%20where%20they%20could%20relax%20in%20the%20evenings%20and%20enjoy%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%