e.%20Her%20book%20details%20vivid%20memories%20of%20their%20time%20together%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20enjoyable%20for%20her%20being%20in%201934%20when%20Mahi%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20Bagari%20range%20of%20the%20(then)%20Kaziranga%20game%20sanctuary%20with%20headquarters%20at%20Golaghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahi%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F239958%2Fassam-manas-national-park-former-poachers-turn-forest-protectors-rhino-conservation-india-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocused%20on%20curbing%20poaching%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Indira%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20took%20advantage%20of%20the%20time%20to%20familiarise%20herself%20with%20the%20lay%20of%20the%20land.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20night%2C%20wild%20elephants%20raided%20the%20paddy%20fields%20to%20gorge%20on%20the%20ripe%20paddy.%20Occasionally%2C%20one%20of%20them%20would%20venture%20into%20the%20bungalow%20and%20noisily%20scratch%20its%20neck%20on%20one%20of%20the%20wooden%20posts%20supporting%20the%20building.%20I%20was%20too%20afraid%20to%20be%20able%20to%20sleep.%20The%20first%20couple%20of%20months%20in%20Baguri%2C%20I%20lived%20in%20constant%20fear%20of%20the%20forest%20and%20its%20wild%20beasts.%20But%2C%20slowly%2C%20I%20grew%20to%20love%20the%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCy3KL4oPmw9%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCy3KL4oPmw9%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%